OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FWhile the football world focuses on
OL,7,Fthe World Cup, player agents and club
OL,8,Fexecutives in the Midlands are busy
OL,9,Flining up transfers for the domestic
OL,10,Fseason which starts next month.
OL,12,FSome business has already happened and
OL,13,Fthere is much more to come.
OL,15,FThis is where our Premier League and
OL,16,FChampionship clubs are right now:
OL,18,FASTON VILLA:
OL,20,FIN: Modou Cisse (LASK, #5m)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
