OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FThe big story this summer could be
OL,7,FMorgan Rogers and whether Arsenal's
OL,8,Finterest turns into a transfer. That
OL,9,Fwould give Villa some financial
OL,10,Fbreathing space to improve the squad.
OL,12,FNOTTINGHAM FOREST:
OL,14,FOUT: Elliot Anderson (Manchester City,
OL,15,F#116m), David Carmo (Olympiacos,
OL,16,F#7.7m), Angus Gunn (SJ Earthquakes,
OL,17,Ffree), Stefan Ortega (free), Willy
OL,18,FBoly (free)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/15
