OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FNottingham Forest haven't signed
OL,7,Fanyone yet but they've done by far and
OL,8,Faway the best piece of business. The
OL,9,Fsale of Elliot Anderson to Manchester
OL,10,FCity for #116m is a record for an
OL,11,FEnglish player and all the more
OL,12,Fremarkable as they bought him for just
OL,13,F#35m two years ago.
OL,15,FIncomings have understandably been
OL,16,Fslow because new head coach Oliver
OL,17,FGlasner was only appointed this week.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
