CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FThey will sign a replacement for
OL,7,FAnderson and two or three more in the
OL,8,Fcoming weeks but it's unlikely to be
OL,9,Fas crazy as some of their past windows.
OL,11,FSporting director Matteo Tognozzi
OL,12,Fwatched Argentina v Egypt at the World
OL,13,FCup this week so it's likely someone
OL,14,Fis of interest in one of those squads.
OL,16,FCOVENTRY CITY:
OL,18,FIN: Frank Onyeka (Brentford, #6m)
OL,20,FOUT: Jamie Allen (free), Brad Collins
OL,21,F(free)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
