OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FCoventry City made the loan signing of
OL,7,FFrank Onyeka permanent but are yet to
OL,8,Fmake any improvements to their squad
OL,9,Fto cope with life in the Premier
OL,10,FLeague.
OL,12,FThey are trying to do the same with
OL,13,FBrighton goalkeeper Carl Rushworth -
OL,14,Fhe said he would want to stay if he
OL,15,Fwon promotion and he's true to his
OL,16,Fword. The big question is whether the
OL,17,Fclubs can agree a fee.
OL,19,FBIRMINGHAM CITY:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/15
