OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FIN: Dael Fry (free), Jhon Solis
OL,7,F(Girona, #6.9m)
OL,9,FOUT: Jonathan Panzo (free)
OL,11,FBirmingham City are looking for a
OL,12,Fcalmer summer than previous years
OL,13,Funder owners Knighthead. Since Chris
OL,14,FDavies took over two years ago there
OL,15,Fhave been 80 players coming in and out.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/15
