OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FThey didn't trouble the play-offs last
OL,7,Fseason in part because of a lack of
OL,8,Fphysicality and Championship
OL,9,Fexperience. They've tried to address
OL,10,Fthat early with the signing of Dael
OL,11,FFry from Middlesbrough.
OL,13,FDERBY COUNTY:
OL,15,FIN: Bobby Clark (RB Salzburg, #6m)
OL,17,FOUT: Callum Elder (Lincoln City,
OL,18,Ffree), Ben Osborn (free), Andreas
OL,19,FWeimann (free), Jake Rooney (free),
OL,20,FDanny Batth (free)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/15
