PN,34509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FThe permanent signing of attacking
OL,7,Fmidfielder Bobby Clark will please
OL,8,FDerby County supporters and there is
OL,9,Fplenty more work to do this summer.
OL,11,FThe spine of the team needs
OL,12,Freinforcing with a defender, a
OL,13,Fmidfielder and striker required. They
OL,14,Fare interested in Manchester City
OL,15,Fstriker Divin Mubama - who played for
OL,16,FStoke City last year.
OL,18,FThey may well look to cash in on
OL,19,Fgoalkeeper Jacob Widell Zetterstrom
OL,20,Fwhose value has rocketed since
OL,21,Fstarring for Sweden at the World Cup.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
