OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FThe elephant in the room is the
OL,7,Fpotential investment from Saudi
OL,8,FArabian billionaire Turki Alalshikh -
OL,9,Fthat could change everything should it
OL,10,Fgo ahead.
OL,12,FSTOKE CITY:
OL,14,FIN: Ethan Galbraith (Swansea City,
OL,15,F#10m), Djibril Soumare (Braga, #3.5m),
OL,16,FLuke Graham (Dundee FC, #2m), Svante
OL,17,FIngelsson (Sheff Wed, #1m), Josh
OL,18,FGriffiths (West Brom, #600k)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
