OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FOUT: Lewis Baker (Bursaspor, free),
OL,7,FNikola Jojic (free), Steven Nzonzi
OL,8,F(free)
OL,10,FStoke City are the busiest club in the
OL,11,FMidlands this summer with five
OL,12,Fsignings already. The big money
OL,13,Farrival of midfielder Ethan Galbraith
OL,14,Fhas caught the headlines, although we
OL,15,Funderstand Swansea will only get near
OL,16,F#10m if significant bonuses are met.
OL,17,FThe initial fee is much lower.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/15
