OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FHe is one of four players arriving
OL,7,Fwith Championship experience -
OL,8,Fincluding Sheffield Wednesday's player
OL,9,Fof the season Svante Ingelsson.
OL,11,FWEST BROMWICH ALBION:
OL,13,FIN: Barney Stewart (Falkirk, #1m),
OL,14,FJimmy-Jay Morgan (Chelsea, #1m), Matt
OL,15,FIngram (Oxford Utd, #200k)
OL,17,FOUT: Josh Griffiths (Stoke City,
OL,18,F#600k), Jed Wallace (Bristol City,
OL,19,Ffree), Daryl Dike (free), Joe
OL,20,FWildsmith (free)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/15
