CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FWest Bromwich Albion are finally free
OL,7,Fof the extreme spending restrictions
OL,8,Fprofit and sustainability rules put
OL,9,Fthem under but that doesn't mean a
OL,10,Fsummer splurge is on the way. The most
OL,11,Fsignificant investment could well be
OL,12,Fin a striker.
OL,14,FThe club have been linked with
OL,15,FSouthampton forward Cameron Archer but
OL,16,FAlbion are likely to look elsewhere.
OL,18,FIN: Raul Jimenez (free), Kieran
OL,19,FTrippier (free)
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783633273
OL,3,CWho are the big football transfers in
OL,4,Cthe Midlands?
OL,6,FOUT: Matt Doherty (free), Dexter
OL,7,FLembikisa (free)
OL,9,FWolves caught the eye with their early
OL,10,Fadditions but there is much work to
OL,11,Fdo. The return of striker Raul Jimenez
OL,12,Fon a free transfer was exciting enough
OL,13,Fand then he starred at the World Cup -
OL,14,Fshowing his best form for years. If he
OL,15,Fkeeps that up he could break a
OL,16,FChampionship scoring record.
OL,18,FFormer England international Kieran
OL,19,FTrippier is another big name and
OL,20,Fshould stand out at this level.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
